# Plotter

## Description
Plotter is a program that can be used to help simulate dislocations or to create normal graphs in either 2D or 3D!

Here is an example of what this program can do!

![Image of 2D plot](data:image/png;base64,%0A)

## Dependencies
To run this program, you need to install the libraries Ipyvolume, Matplotlib, and Seaborn.
